Diagram PNGs on Volusion: /v/vspfiles/sectional-diagrams/{Style}-SC-{code}.png

Regenerate all from Palliser PDFs (auto page find, no per-config editing):
  tools/sectional-diagrams/export_diagrams.ps1
or:  python tools/sectional-diagrams/export_sectional_diagrams.py --publish

When adding a NEW style: add rows here + one block in tools/sectional-diagrams/catalog.json (palliser model/style + pdf name).
